				Saba Grape Mosto Reduction			


Saba has been crafted in Sardinia since ancient times. Our saba is the result of a extensive and careful reduction of the grape must.  
Efisio recommends serving saba with meats, desserts, and other sauces.
 



Saba Grape Mosto Reduction, 11 oz Bottle

