					SARDINIAN CACETTO CHEESE
				


				The Sardinian Cacetto cheese is a typical cheese from Sardinia, produced with pasteurized sheep and goat milk.
It is a mixed cheese with a soft paste; it has a savoury and intense taste that acquires spicy marks in the seasoned cheese.
			











