					TRUFFLE MOLITERNO - 0,6 KG
				


				Typical table or grated cheese, the Pecorino of Moliterno rich taste boats in the particular buds notes of black truffle (Tuber Aestivum).The tradition sees the birth of this cheese in Basilicata, in the area of Moliterno , but now, most of the production is in Sardinia.
			











